{"type": "article", "id": 22388, "title": "像微颤树叶的屏风", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-17T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061540347xC6MlupJ0nRAwoF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本设计师仓本仁(Jin Kuramoto) 带来的一组屏风，一共5种，取名“风”（wind）。屏风的形状都是不规则的，边角圆润，有微微倾斜的角度，因而有些近似在风中微颤的树叶。它使用隔音面料制作，但并不能完全遮挡，有很强的装饰性和一种自然的意境。设计师称屏风的颜色和形状源于雪花、蜂窝以及叶子，它提醒人们关注自然的美好。<a href=\"http://www.jinkuramoto.com/project/wind-offecct/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154032bJ04MFeLAU5anWVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154032LQJGwpmaWUFfNk2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154032GLfI49vhgRoO1ej5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154033ODuv8yIbALZsgc06.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154033MOGnhSslDtZIi8Hk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}